# Cinematic brand UI

## Colors & typography
- UI: `PiligrimColors`, `PiligrimTextStyles`, `piligrimTheme`.
- Font: Museo Sans 300/700 only — no new families / Google Fonts.

## Interaction & surfaces
- Brand taps: `PiligrimTap`, not default `InkWell` ripples.
- Cards: reuse `piligrimCardDecoration()` from `piligrim_card.dart` before new decorations.
- Warm CTAs: `EmberCta` / ember palette — avoid generic Material button restyling.

## Home & atmosphere
- Home: calm cinematic layers (`PiligrimBackground`, ambient/hero widgets) — no neon, no glass unless `kHomeLayeredBlurGlass` is intentionally enabled.
- Heavy `CustomPaint`: prefer `RepaintBoundary`; decorative overlays: `IgnorePointer`.
- Preserve existing motion/parallax structure unless the task is explicitly about performance or animation.

## Reuse before create
Search `lib/widgets/` (`piligrim_*`, `home_*`, `ember_*`, `ErrorView`) before adding a new component.

## Splash
Splash uses explicit `AnimationController` + `Interval` — do not casually migrate it to `flutter_animate`.
